    android.view.View.OnTouchListener

    public class TouchAwareSwipeDismissTouchListener
extends SwipeDismissTouchListener
    Adds touch events to the SwipeDismissTouchListener. Note: The SwipeDismissTouchListener requires API level 12 or later due to use of ViewPropertyAnimator.
